 @{" " link "'#toc0'/MAIN"}Name tzxlist - Sinclair ZX Spectrum "real" tape file lister @{" " link "'#toc1'/MAIN"}Synopsis @{"b"}tzxlist@{"ub"} @{"i"}tapefile@{"ui"}... 

@{" " link "'#toc2'/MAIN"}Description Tzxlist outputs a description of the contents of TZX, TAP and Warajevo TAP tape files. @{" " link "'#toc3'/MAIN"}Options @{"i"}tapefile@{"ui"} specifies a tape file whose contents are to be listed. @{" " link "'#toc4'/MAIN"}Bugs None known. @{" " link "'#toc5'/MAIN"}See Also @{" " link "'fuse.1'/MAIN"}@{"i"}fuse@{"ui"}(1) , @{" " link "'fuse-utils.1'/MAIN"}@{"i"}fuse-utils@{"ui"}(1) , @{" " link "'listbasic.1'/MAIN"}@{"i"}listbasic@{"ui"}(1) , @{" " link "'tapeconv.1'/MAIN"}@{"i"}tapeconv@{"ui"}(1) 

The comp.sys.sinclair Spectrum FAQ, at 
@{" " link "'http://www.worldofspectrum.org/faq/index.html.guide/MAIN"}@{"i"}http://www.worldofspectrum.org/faq/index.html@{"ui"}. @{" " link "'#toc6'/MAIN"}Author Philip Kendall (philip-fuse@shadowmagic.org.uk). 

